WEBVTT

01:41.840 --> 01:42.640
Ji Ling!

01:44.720 --> 01:45.960
Hide!

01:49.920 --> 01:51.160
Where are the prayer beads?

01:51.960 --> 01:53.640
I've moved them to a place

01:53.720 --> 01:56.240
<i>where you'll never ever find them.</i>

02:00.240 --> 02:01.680
Tie them up with the Demon-Binding Rope!

02:01.760 --> 02:02.600
-Yes, sir.
-Yes, sir.

05:24.440 --> 05:27.200
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

05:54.920 --> 05:56.120
Let me do it.

06:14.960 --> 06:16.880
‎-Bravo!
‎-Bravo!

06:27.600 --> 06:28.880
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

06:32.840 --> 06:33.760
Bravo!

08:12.240 --> 08:14.760
-Had a bad dream?
-No.

08:15.800 --> 08:19.240
I was just recalling a lot of the past.

08:20.160 --> 08:23.160
So long ago, feels like a past life.

08:23.760 --> 08:24.760
Yeah.

08:25.720 --> 08:27.040
Over a thousand years.

08:28.320 --> 08:30.720
That's many ordinary lifetimes.

08:33.520 --> 08:34.360
Wangyan,

08:35.559 --> 08:36.400
do we really

08:37.440 --> 08:38.919
have to kill Ji Ling?

08:43.400 --> 08:44.680
Didn't you say

08:44.760 --> 08:46.760
Ji Ling isn't the Dragon Deity?

09:17.440 --> 09:19.280
TOKEN OF SCALES

09:25.560 --> 09:27.320
You haven't changed.

09:27.400 --> 09:30.280
Every time you can't sleep,
you come to my place.

09:33.320 --> 09:36.360
Hui. You did good in every mission.

09:37.400 --> 09:38.760
This is your reward.

09:45.880 --> 09:47.440
Thank you, Master.

09:49.440 --> 09:51.480
I already have so many colorful stones.

09:52.280 --> 09:54.120
The other sisters don't have any!

10:00.560 --> 10:01.800
What's wrong?

10:02.440 --> 10:03.480
Master,

10:04.360 --> 10:05.560
has the Dragon Deity

10:07.440 --> 10:09.320
truly been corrupted by evil thoughts?

10:12.480 --> 10:16.200
Nothing in this world
is purely good or evil.

10:17.160 --> 10:19.840
<i>Be it human, demon,</i>

10:20.400 --> 10:23.240
<i>deity, or even devil,</i>

10:23.800 --> 10:25.920
<i>all have a hidden side.</i>

10:27.080 --> 10:30.480
<i>The brighter the light,</i>
<i>the darker the shadow it casts.</i>

10:31.800 --> 10:35.040
<i>Demons can wear painted skin,</i>
<i>humans can wear masks.</i>

10:35.840 --> 10:37.920
<i>Even deities have their obsessions.</i>

10:47.960 --> 10:49.080
Wangyan.

11:08.280 --> 11:11.720
BY WANGYUE

11:15.000 --> 11:16.440
<i>Over a hundred years,</i>

11:17.520 --> 11:20.320
<i>I've done many things with you</i>
<i>that we had no choice in.</i>

11:20.960 --> 11:22.760
<i>Though we meant to stay pure,</i>

11:23.400 --> 11:27.760
<i>our hands are stained with blood,</i>
<i>and our hearts are full of guilt.</i>

11:56.480 --> 11:58.640
Wangyan, let's go.

12:03.720 --> 12:06.160
Wangyan, let's go.

12:15.920 --> 12:18.000
<i>This mission is dangerous.</i>

12:18.080 --> 12:21.520
<i>I know you've developed</i>
<i>feelings for Ji Ling.</i>

12:22.560 --> 12:24.840
<i>Whether he is the Dragon Deity or not,</i>

12:24.920 --> 12:26.240
<i>it's a hard choice for you.</i>

12:28.000 --> 12:32.040
<i>I don't want to see you</i>
<i>torn between duty to the world</i>

12:32.760 --> 12:35.200
<i>and drawing blood against your beloved.</i>

12:36.280 --> 12:39.240
<i>Take care of yourself. I'll be back.</i>

13:11.760 --> 13:13.760
I've been waiting for you.

13:14.600 --> 13:16.440
The Oracle Stone has a new prophecy.

13:17.120 --> 13:18.480
It says…

13:21.200 --> 13:22.840
the Dragon Deity will fall.

13:25.760 --> 13:29.480
I'm not that easy to kill.

13:30.720 --> 13:31.760
"Won't die"

13:33.000 --> 13:34.440
and "not easy to kill"

13:35.160 --> 13:36.480
are two different things.

13:38.560 --> 13:39.960
What are you trying to say?

13:41.160 --> 13:43.800
You wanted to take back
your power from Xiaowei,

13:44.520 --> 13:46.520
so you sent Li Jie to the Wei mansion.

13:47.480 --> 13:48.480
But you wouldn't risk your life,

13:49.160 --> 13:52.440
so you sent a puppet instead, Ji Ling,

13:52.520 --> 13:56.520
to go with Li Jie in your place. Right?

13:58.960 --> 14:01.480
When I saw Ji Ling at the Wei mansion,

14:01.560 --> 14:02.640
I was surprised.

14:03.320 --> 14:07.440
I thought you were just pretending
to be some innocent, lively young man,

14:07.520 --> 14:09.640
acting like you didn't know me.

14:10.640 --> 14:14.080
You're the hunter commander
of the Shilin Sect. And you?

14:14.920 --> 14:16.400
What exactly are you?

14:18.640 --> 14:19.560
Me?

14:21.800 --> 14:25.040
Just an ordinary hunter, no flower
on my forehead. What's wrong?

14:25.840 --> 14:27.560
Were you joking,

14:27.640 --> 14:29.000
or were you serious?

14:29.720 --> 14:32.240
Not until Xiaowei gravely wounded Ji Ling

14:37.680 --> 14:40.320
and the wound's edge showed wood chips.

14:41.960 --> 14:43.640
I figured Ji Ling and Li Jie

14:43.720 --> 14:45.960
might run into
a Formless Moon member there.

14:47.000 --> 14:48.720
I just didn't expect it to be you,

14:49.360 --> 14:50.800
of all people.

14:52.280 --> 14:54.000
When things are too coincidental,

14:55.160 --> 14:56.920
someone's usually pulling the strings.

14:58.000 --> 15:00.680
The Fox Queen
specifically sent Wuyi and me.

15:00.760 --> 15:02.680
She knows about Ji Ling.

15:03.480 --> 15:07.840
She said Ji Ling and Wuyi are fated ones.

15:08.480 --> 15:09.840
What does that mean?

15:10.720 --> 15:12.280
Fated ones?

15:14.120 --> 15:17.040
Now, your power has passed to Wu Shiguang.

15:17.120 --> 15:18.560
Only one piece, for now,

15:18.640 --> 15:20.520
not enough to seal your fate.

15:21.720 --> 15:23.640
But the Oracle Stone never errs.

15:25.480 --> 15:28.440
The Dragon Deity's fall
will come, sooner or later.

15:29.880 --> 15:32.040
That's why I need your help.

15:33.520 --> 15:34.760
What do you want me to do?

15:35.440 --> 15:37.000
Get close to Wu Shiguang.

15:37.680 --> 15:39.520
Find a way to take the prayer beads

15:40.280 --> 15:41.400
and bring them to me.

15:43.200 --> 15:44.600
Those beads know their owner.

15:45.280 --> 15:48.320
Taking them won't be easy.

15:51.760 --> 15:55.360
Foxes from the Formless Moon
are masters at seduction.

15:56.080 --> 16:00.480
A mere Wu Shiguang
shouldn't be too hard for you.

16:04.160 --> 16:05.160
Right.

16:08.640 --> 16:09.920
For a thousand years,

16:10.440 --> 16:12.520
I've played countless roles,

16:13.440 --> 16:15.080
had countless family,

16:16.200 --> 16:17.200
lovers,

16:18.840 --> 16:19.880
and dearest friends.

16:21.880 --> 16:25.400
But truth and lies blur,
this life is but a dream.

16:26.600 --> 16:29.000
I can barely remember who I am anymore.

16:31.000 --> 16:31.840
You're tired?

16:42.080 --> 16:42.960
What about you?

16:45.320 --> 16:46.600
Wearing a skin

16:47.280 --> 16:48.760
for too long,

16:50.040 --> 16:52.840
you'll forget the heart beneath.

16:54.840 --> 16:55.960
But the heart

16:57.400 --> 16:59.760
always remembers who it truly is.

17:14.720 --> 17:16.440
I hope this is the last time.

17:17.920 --> 17:19.160
Trust me,

17:20.760 --> 17:22.480
this is the last time.

17:23.400 --> 17:27.560
After this, you and everyone
in the Formless Moon

17:28.840 --> 17:30.040
will be truly free.

17:39.600 --> 17:42.560
Wu Shiguang, do something!

17:42.640 --> 17:44.360
Wu Shiguang? Wu Shiguang?

17:57.960 --> 17:59.280
I rubbed it off!

17:59.360 --> 18:00.400
I rubbed the rope loose!

18:01.160 --> 18:02.000
My spell did that.

18:04.880 --> 18:07.400
Why… Why didn't you use that sooner?

18:07.480 --> 18:08.800
My bones are stiff!

18:08.880 --> 18:10.320
You're a weasel.

18:10.400 --> 18:13.360
Your bones are the softest in the world.
Stop playing the victim.

18:13.440 --> 18:14.840
You just make up rumors out of thin air!

18:18.440 --> 18:19.920
What now?

19:04.720 --> 19:05.760
Indeed,

19:06.320 --> 19:08.080
a weasel's fart really does work best.

19:08.160 --> 19:10.160
Can you stop with the rumors?

19:12.280 --> 19:14.640
That's black smoke from my blade, alright?

19:16.880 --> 19:18.560
So? Praise me!

19:19.400 --> 19:20.240
Hello?

19:33.680 --> 19:35.320
Be careful!

19:35.400 --> 19:37.360
I don't want to vanish into thin air.

19:39.640 --> 19:41.200
What are you doing? I'm here.

19:57.880 --> 19:59.760
Commander Li, as you instructed,

19:59.840 --> 20:01.360
I let them escape.

20:01.440 --> 20:02.560
What now?

20:03.920 --> 20:04.960
Follow them.

20:05.720 --> 20:07.480
He'll definitely go get the prayer beads.

21:30.840 --> 21:32.360
Didn't you go back to the Formless Moon?

21:33.360 --> 21:36.760
The moment we parted, I couldn't sleep.

21:36.840 --> 21:39.360
I told myself I shouldn't think of you,

21:40.080 --> 21:41.280
and I can't think of you.

21:42.160 --> 21:47.360
But when feelings arise,
the heart follows.

21:48.080 --> 21:49.280
So I had to come find you.

21:51.000 --> 21:53.080
Formless Moon foxes are truly something.

21:54.000 --> 21:55.360
You make tracking someone

21:55.920 --> 21:58.400
-sound so seductive.
-Seductive?

22:15.960 --> 22:17.440
You've misunderstood me, sir.

22:18.560 --> 22:20.400
The one tracking you isn't me.

22:21.480 --> 22:22.720
It's Li Jie.

22:52.760 --> 22:53.880
He meant to let us go.

22:55.040 --> 22:57.240
Ye Changsheng doesn't need a token on him.

22:59.600 --> 23:00.840
Exactly.

23:01.800 --> 23:04.360
I trapped him in my maze formation

23:04.440 --> 23:08.400
or else Li Jie would've caught you by now.

23:31.640 --> 23:33.280
Instead of thanking me,

23:34.600 --> 23:37.960
you nearly deflowered me.

23:38.840 --> 23:41.360
Nearly cut you. Don't talk nonsense,

23:42.440 --> 23:44.160
and that's what your name implies.

23:47.080 --> 23:48.000
So why are you here?

23:48.600 --> 23:49.840
To help you.

23:51.560 --> 23:52.960
I'm used to going solo.

23:53.600 --> 23:54.880
I don't need your help.

23:55.680 --> 23:57.080
Killing the Dragon Deity

23:57.920 --> 24:00.000
is no easy task.

24:02.000 --> 24:04.320
You sure you don't need help?

24:05.840 --> 24:07.080
I'm killing him

24:07.960 --> 24:10.000
to avenge my entire clan.

24:11.640 --> 24:12.680
What about you?

24:15.480 --> 24:17.560
The Oracle Stone gave a prophecy.

24:18.880 --> 24:20.120
I have no choice.

24:23.680 --> 24:25.280
You're a cunning fox,

24:26.080 --> 24:27.760
always deceiving and running off.

24:28.920 --> 24:29.800
Why should I trust you?

24:30.720 --> 24:32.920
Have I ever deceived you?

24:33.720 --> 24:34.800
Back at the Wei mansion,

24:34.880 --> 24:36.920
who claimed to be after Xiaowei

24:37.720 --> 24:39.200
but ended up wounded by me?

24:42.080 --> 24:43.880
That was to help you.

24:45.320 --> 24:46.840
Lu Wuyi's not easy to fool.

24:46.920 --> 24:48.720
Wangyan, are you okay?

24:49.320 --> 24:52.600
You wanted to buy time
for those Shilin Sect hunters.

24:52.680 --> 24:55.960
So I pretended you wounded me,
to hold my sister back.

25:00.040 --> 25:02.400
That hit of yours was pretty hard.

25:03.520 --> 25:05.400
And now you blame me?

25:06.360 --> 25:07.800
You even deceive your own sister.

25:09.520 --> 25:11.200
I didn't want to deceive her either.

25:11.920 --> 25:15.680
But that move isn't just for Xiaowei,
it's for you.

25:18.920 --> 25:20.640
You're in my heart.

25:22.880 --> 25:26.120
And I know you have feelings for me too.

25:38.320 --> 25:40.280
Your heart's racing.

25:44.760 --> 25:45.640
Want to work together?

25:46.520 --> 25:47.760
Show your cards.

25:49.200 --> 25:50.200
What do you have?

25:53.800 --> 25:55.200
That depends

25:57.560 --> 25:58.680
on what you want.

26:00.440 --> 26:01.560
I want to know

26:02.600 --> 26:04.280
where the next piece
of Dragon Deity's Power is.

26:36.280 --> 26:38.080
<i>I've been dreading telling you this,</i>

26:38.880 --> 26:40.320
<i>but Wangyue has also turned.</i>

26:42.320 --> 26:44.560
I know you two are like sisters.

26:45.120 --> 26:49.360
So, go find her, uncover the truth,

26:50.480 --> 26:53.320
or perhaps help her find her way back.

26:54.320 --> 26:57.600
Master, I will find out the truth

26:58.160 --> 27:00.560
and prove she hasn't betrayed us.

27:02.240 --> 27:03.200
Wangyan.

27:31.400 --> 27:33.720
You blame me for liking Ji Ling.

27:34.800 --> 27:36.320
But you're into someone too.

27:38.080 --> 27:40.000
Helping him gather
the Dragon Deity's Power

27:40.080 --> 27:41.160
was a mission from our master.

27:44.160 --> 27:45.120
Really?

27:46.560 --> 27:47.600
Of course.

27:53.640 --> 27:55.480
Ji Ling is innocent and kind.

27:56.400 --> 27:57.880
I do like him.

27:59.600 --> 28:01.200
But right now,
the greater good comes first.

28:01.800 --> 28:02.600
I understand that.

28:03.640 --> 28:06.560
Besides, he's not the Dragon Deity.

28:07.320 --> 28:10.880
It's the Dragon Deity turning evil,
destined to fall.

28:11.920 --> 28:14.000
Ji Ling was just deceived.

28:15.360 --> 28:16.600
He'll understand me.

28:22.880 --> 28:26.080
Wangyan, don't leave me behind again.

28:28.120 --> 28:29.360
I won't.

28:30.440 --> 28:32.240
No matter where,

28:32.960 --> 28:34.280
we'll be together.

28:47.720 --> 28:53.000
Wangyan, why are you so fragrant today?

28:55.000 --> 28:56.040
Do I?

28:58.080 --> 29:00.920
Maybe just the grass damp with night dew.

31:14.360 --> 31:15.760
I'm real.

31:48.400 --> 31:51.520
<i>I don't understand love, nor hate.</i>

31:52.040 --> 31:54.160
<i>I don't think I've ever loved anyone</i>

31:54.240 --> 31:56.480
<i>or hated anyone either.</i>

31:57.960 --> 31:59.120
<i>I guess</i>

31:59.200 --> 32:01.280
<i>-I'm just…</i>
<i>-A woodenhead.</i>

32:04.600 --> 32:07.600
<i>Fine, I'm a woodenhead then.</i>

32:09.480 --> 32:10.600
<i>No, you're not.</i>

32:35.840 --> 32:37.120
Master Dragon Deity.

32:40.240 --> 32:41.160
I…

32:44.360 --> 32:45.200
I…

32:55.200 --> 32:56.440
Master Chi Wen.

32:57.880 --> 32:58.920
Wu Shiguang said

33:00.480 --> 33:02.160
I'm a puppet.

33:03.880 --> 33:06.920
But I'm clearly a fox from South Mountain.

33:07.720 --> 33:09.480
There must be some mistake,

33:10.760 --> 33:11.800
right?

33:14.040 --> 33:15.560
So you found out.

33:17.600 --> 33:19.880
You are indeed a puppet I made.

33:21.640 --> 33:22.880
Not a fox.

33:24.080 --> 33:25.360
No… No way.

33:27.160 --> 33:28.600
It's not true.

33:29.200 --> 33:32.320
I was born on South Mountain,
in a cave by Yumian Lake.

33:33.160 --> 33:35.080
<i>I was a blind fox.</i>

33:35.680 --> 33:39.200
<i>Outside the cave,</i>
<i>there were lots of raspberries</i>

33:39.880 --> 33:41.520
<i>and wood sorrel.</i>

33:42.200 --> 33:45.040
Then, I was hit by falling rocks

33:45.720 --> 33:46.800
and was about to die.

33:46.880 --> 33:49.520
You saved me and healed my eyes.

33:50.200 --> 33:52.840
<i>You even gave me power</i>
<i>and sent me to save people.</i>

33:53.640 --> 33:55.200
I remember all of this.

33:55.760 --> 33:57.280
How could I possibly be…

33:58.120 --> 33:59.360
a puppet?

34:00.320 --> 34:02.080
If I can give you power,

34:04.600 --> 34:06.360
I can also give you memories.

34:08.480 --> 34:09.520
Give me…

34:12.760 --> 34:13.880
memories?

34:20.320 --> 34:21.360
So,

34:25.719 --> 34:27.360
all of it is fake?

34:29.280 --> 34:30.639
You made it all up?

34:32.600 --> 34:36.719
In this world, there never was
a blind fox like me?

34:39.040 --> 34:40.360
No Ji Ling?

34:43.360 --> 34:44.639
Is that true?

34:50.440 --> 34:51.840
Master…

34:53.199 --> 34:55.920
why did you create someone like me…

34:59.320 --> 35:00.520
a puppet?

35:03.000 --> 35:04.640
Are you blaming me?

35:08.600 --> 35:13.200
I granted you life
to experience the human world.

35:14.920 --> 35:16.480
Isn't that a gift?

35:17.400 --> 35:19.760
Being a puppet, controlled,

35:21.880 --> 35:25.640
deceived by my most trusted,
my dearest one…

35:26.800 --> 35:29.400
-You call that a gift?
-Don't be insolent.

35:31.680 --> 35:33.040
Master,

35:33.840 --> 35:35.480
did you create me

35:36.720 --> 35:39.520
just to have a puppet
you could manipulate at will?

35:41.000 --> 35:42.920
Or did you need someone

35:43.760 --> 35:45.320
who could die in your place anytime?

35:49.840 --> 35:52.120
-Does it matter?
-Yes, it matters!

35:53.400 --> 35:56.720
To me, it matters a lot!

35:59.520 --> 36:01.360
Even if I'm a puppet,

36:02.200 --> 36:04.440
I want to know why I exist!

36:05.560 --> 36:07.200
Even as a puppet,

36:08.360 --> 36:10.800
if I can protect you,

36:11.440 --> 36:13.560
then my existence has meaning!

36:14.560 --> 36:16.440
Then I'm not just a piece of wood!

36:18.080 --> 36:20.560
I'm my own unique self!

36:22.520 --> 36:24.280
I am Ji Ling!

36:27.640 --> 36:29.600
I am Ji Ling…

36:36.520 --> 36:39.440
I… I am Ji Ling…

36:57.160 --> 36:58.240
Follow me.

37:30.960 --> 37:32.720
<i>How will I find you?</i>

37:34.360 --> 37:37.160
<i>Don't worry. I will find you.</i>

38:13.880 --> 38:17.200
Still think you're unique?

38:32.480 --> 38:36.680
I always hoped
you could stay innocent forever,

38:37.280 --> 38:38.680
living a carefree life.

38:40.040 --> 38:41.760
You're the piece of my youth, my past,

38:42.960 --> 38:44.440
that I most wanted to keep.

38:46.800 --> 38:47.840
What a pity.
